title: Pure Prairie League - Two Lane Highway (1975 quad mix 24/96 loss
description:
Pure Prairie League - Two Lane Highway (1975 quad/surround mix 24/96 lossless 4.0 DVD-A)

24/96 4.0 lossless MLP (DVD-Audio).
16/48 4.0 DTS @ 1536kbps (DVD-Video) for compatibility with standard DVD players.

Converted from quad CD-4 vinyl using an AUDIO TECHNICA AT20SLa CD-4 cartridge / JVC 4DD-5 demodulator.
 
 
"Agreeably quiet and modest blends of pop-rock songs with C&W arrangements. (On) Two Lane Highway, the group honed it's earlier approaches, beefed up the guitars and ivestigated related stylings for greater variety." ****
- Charley Walters, Rolling Stone
